OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTwitter to stop users      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flinking to big social      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fplatforms                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Twitter says it will shut down accounts
OL,6, solely designed to promote other big   
OL,7, social media platforms, or which link  
OL,8, off to or contain usernames from them. 
OL,10,FThe move affects content from platforms
OL,11,Fincluding Facebook, Instagram,         
OL,12,FMastodon, Truth Social, Tribel, Nostr  
OL,13,Fand Post, the company said in a tweet. 
OL,15,FBut cross-content posting from other   
OL,16,Fsites will still be allowed.           
OL,18,FFormer Twitter boss Jack Dorsey, who   
OL,19,Frecently invested in Nostr, replied to 
OL,20,Fthe Twitter post with one word: "Why?".
